                            <comment id="17421577" author="emilles" created="Tue, 28 Sep 2021 17:50:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This could be fixed on the Micronaut side by adding a type argument:&lt;br/&gt;
  &lt;tt&gt;interface ConversionService&amp;lt;Impl extends ConversionService&amp;lt;?&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the signature parser is not properly rendering the raw type &lt;tt&gt;ConversionService&lt;/tt&gt; (or &lt;tt&gt;AC&lt;/tt&gt; in the example).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
